## Third-Party Licenses

This project depends on the following open-source packages:

### Python Dependencies

- **openpyxl** (MIT License)
  Copyright (c) openpyxl developers
  https://pypi.org/project/openpyxl/

- **pandas** (BSD 3-Clause License)
  Copyright (c) pandas developers
  https://pypi.org/project/pandas/

- **numpy** (BSD License)
  Copyright (c) 2005-2025, NumPy Developers
  https://pypi.org/project/numpy/

- **scipy** (BSD License)
  Copyright (c) 2001-2002 Enthought, Inc. 2003, SciPy Developers
  https://pypi.org/project/scipy/

- **JSBSim** (LGPL 2.1+)
  Copyright (c) JSBSim Development Team
  https://pypi.org/project/JSBSim/
  Note: JSBSim is used as an external library. Users must install JSBSim separately and comply with its LGPL license terms.

### External Tools (Not Included)

- **FlightGear** (GPL-2.0)
  https://www.flightgear.org/
  Note: FlightGear is an optional visualization tool. It is not included in this project.

