## License Compatibility

This project (MIT License) is compatible with all dependencies:
- **MIT** (openpyxl): Fully compatible
- **BSD** (pandas, numpy, scipy): Fully compatible
- **LGPL 2.1+** (JSBSim): Compatible when used as external library (dynamic linking)

Users are responsible for complying with the licenses of dependencies they choose to install.
